    Title: I Ching
  Title: The Man of Many Qualities
Title: Organizational Growth Pains
---
The rise of the state out of disorder is marked by struggles. The period of
growth requires caution against premature moves and perseverance to overcome
attendant obstacles and confusion. Helpers need be appointed.
